title: Worst Date Wednesday: Doesn't It Feel Like We're in Paris?
description: Kiersten went on a date with a guy at a bowling alley parking lot.  When she got there it turns out he had been drinking all day already.  It only gets worse from there when she eventually meets his parents at the end of the date.
